headline.main: LATEST IRAQ UPSET IS ECHO OF REVOLT; Fall of Al-Midfai Cabinet Laid to Public Refusal to Condone Intrigue With Nazis

lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM, Oct. 10 -- The latest ministerial crisis in Iraq, according to a reliable observer who has just arrived in Jerusalem, developed from the circumstances succeeding Rashid All el Gailani's ill-starred attempt to remove Iraq from traditional British influence and bring the nation into the Nazi orbit.
